---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AI Disclaimer" description="Important information about AI-generated content on FutureScopeHub.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <article class="article-content">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8">
          AI Content <span class="text-[var(--color-neon-pink)]">Disclaimer</span>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-galaxy-dark)] to-[var(--color-deep-space)] border border-[var(--color-neon-pink)]/30 mb-10">
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] m-0">
            <strong class="text-white">Transparency Notice:</strong> Content on FutureScopeHub is generated 
            with the assistance of artificial intelligence and reviewed by humans before publication.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>What This Means</h2>
        <p>
          We use Google's Gemini 3 large language models to help synthesize, summarize, and write 
          articles based on information gathered from public sources. While we employ advanced 
          techniques like <strong>Search Grounding</strong> to verify facts, AI systems can still make errors.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Safeguards</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Search Grounding:</strong> Every factual claim is cross-referenced against live Google Search results</li>
          <li><strong>Source Attribution:</strong> We cite our sources whenever possible</li>
          <li><strong>Human Review:</strong> All posts pass through human review before publication</li>
          <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> We actively monitor for and correct errors</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Limitations</h2>
        <p>
          Despite our safeguards, you should be aware that:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>AI may occasionally produce inaccurate or outdated information</li>
          <li>Opinions expressed may not reflect the views of any individual or organization</li>
          <li>This content should not be used as the sole source for important decisions</li>
          <li>We recommend verifying critical information with primary sources</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Report Issues</h2>
        <p>
          Found something wrong? We want to know. Please report factual errors, outdated information, 
          or any concerns to <a href="https://twitter.com/futurescopehub">@FutureScopeHub</a> on Twitter/X.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Why AI?</h2>
        <p>
          We believe AI, used responsibly, can democratize access to quality information synthesis. 
          Not everyone has time to read 50 articles a day. Our AI helps distill the essence while 
          our humans ensure the soul.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-8">
          Last updated: February 2026
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
